Async Swift transport for the SPICE vd_agent protocol over the
virtio-serial port Apple's VZSpiceAgentPortAttachment presents to a
macOS guest.

Depends on SpiceProtocol (also MIT-licensed by Spooky Labs).

No source code from SPICE reference implementations (spice-vdagent,
spice-gtk, utmapp/vd_agent) was copied or derived. The POSIX file
descriptor + termios configuration follows the BSD POSIX conventions
documented in the macOS man pages; behaviour was verified via DeepWiki
queries against utmapp/vd_agent without reading its source.
